## 4. Course objectives 🟢

- Understand the core concepts of big data, distributed storage, and analytics platforms.
- Apply big-data processing techniques to transform and analyse large datasets.
- Develop practical skills in building analytics pipelines and generating actionable insights.
- Design and evaluate scalable, reliable, and ethical analytics solutions.
- Communicate results using dashboards, reports, and data-driven narratives.

